extra test failed at unrelated tests, should not be introduced by this change:
>>create table tlob130ts2 (c1 int not null, c2 blob, primary key (c1));

So I will do full regression by hand in my dev machine.

@DaveBirdsall @selvaganesang could you help to review the code?

@zellerh 
seems you lose a ";" after begin,  if no ";" there will throw syntax error.
so if query like "begin; insert into t1 values(?,?); delete from t2; insert into t2 values (?); end", actually there will have 5 preparedStatements , each do one query.
